text: Yordanka Yovkova (born 8 January 1933) is a Bulgarian gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
